About
=====
This is a drop-in replacement for megaannex. It should be compatible in every way except the initial environment variables

This project makes use of https://github.com/t3rm1n4l/go-mega for the connection to mega.co.nz

Installation
============
git clone https://github.com/dxtr/megaannex-go.git
cd megaannex-go
go build
Rename megaannex-go to git-remote-annex-mega and copy it to your PATH

Usage
=====
Init a remote:
MEGA_USERNAME="<name>" MEGA_PASSWORD="<password>" git annex initremote <name> type=external externaltype=mega encryption=hybrid keyid=<keyid> mac=HMACSHA256 folder=Documents

See the git-annex manual for more options

Issues
